30
00:01:23,447 --> 00:01:24,987
Estou fora.

31
00:01:26,858 --> 00:01:28,365
Vejo-te por aí.

32
00:01:30,231 --> 00:01:31,976
Cuida-te, Ryan.

33
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:35,544
Tu conheces a Alex.

